description: *OFFERS DUE TUESDAY 9/26 @ 3:00pm.  Introducing a lovely single family, perfect for developers, investors, or those seeking homeownership! Nestled in the sought-after neighborhood of South Boston, this attached townhouse-style gem boasts an array of features.  Gleaming hardwood floors and an inviting open floor plan. 2 beds & 1 bath, this residence offers comfort and style. The basement provides a canvas for additional living space and is equipped with plumbing for a convenient half bath. Enjoy the outdoors on the large private deck off the kitchen, leading to a private back yard with many possibilities. Public transportation T/Bus is close, making commuting a breeze. Quick access to the Pike & Rte. 93 ensures convenient travel, all while relishing the perks of South Boston living. Immerse yourself in the vibrant Southie community, with the Seaport District, beaches, shopping and a multitude of dining options just a few blocks away!  Sold "as-is"
